  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loss is a <strong>3D, First-Person, Action, Adventure, Puzzle & Horror</strong> game with actual gameplay! You'll play as a teenage boy, who wakes up one night only to find out that all of his family is gone. Where did they go? Why is he alone? Who are these strange ghosts roaming around the house? While solving this mystery, you will <strong>explore your house, grab items and keys, unlock doors, solve puzzles, go outside to touch some grass, find hidden notes and much more!</strong> Many paranormal beings will ensure that you don't find the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The creatures you'll find are rather aggressive too, so you'll have to fight back! With the help of your flashlight, you can point it at specific enemies for a few seconds to kill them. This exciting combat will always keep you on the edge, and it is a nice change of pace from the slower puzzle-solving sections. <strong>There are multiple weapons and various ghost types to defeat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 2 hours of core gameplay (no Walking Sim)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious house to explore and a secret environment outside...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Puzzles to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple ghost enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 deadly Bosses to defeat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various items and gameplay scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden notes that reveal your family's story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic jump scares</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loss is a <strong>3D, First-Person, Action, Adventure, Puzzle & Horror</strong> game with actual gameplay! You'll play as a teenage boy, who wakes up one night only to find out that all of his family is gone. Where did they go? Why is he alone? Who are these strange ghosts roaming around the house? While solving this mystery, you will <strong>explore your house, grab items and keys, unlock doors, solve puzzles, go outside to touch some grass, find hidden notes and much more!</strong> Many paranormal beings will ensure that you don't find the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The creatures you'll find are rather aggressive too, so you'll have to fight back! With the help of your flashlight, you can point it at specific enemies for a few seconds to kill them. This exciting combat will always keep you on the edge, and it is a nice change of pace from the slower puzzle-solving sections. <strong>There are multiple weapons and various ghost types to defeat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 2 hours of core gameplay (no Walking Sim)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious house to explore and a secret environment outside...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Puzzles to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple ghost enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 deadly Bosses to defeat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various items and gameplay scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden notes that reveal your family's story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic jump scares</p></li></ul>",
